      "heading": "1. Description of the Service",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "EasyIntake App provides a cloud-based software platform designed to help organizations collect, structure, process, and manage information through automated workflows, digital intake forms, and structured application systems."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The Service may include:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "digital intake forms",
            "workflow automation",
            "structured data extraction",
            "application orchestration",
            "document generation",
            "AI-assisted data processing",
            "analytics and reporting",
            "communication tools",
            "APIs and integrations"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "EasyIntake operates solely as a software infrastructure platform."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "EasyIntake does not provide legal, financial, medical, insurance, tax, compliance, or professional advice."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Users are solely responsible for verifying the accuracy and completeness of all information processed through the Service."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
