          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "their interactions with End Users",
            "the legality of data collection",
            "obtaining required user consent",
            "compliance with applicable regulations",
            "verification of submitted information",
            "decisions made based on collected information"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "EasyIntake acts only as a technology provider and does not participate in transactions between Business Users and End Users."
